s gens, donc je ne sais pas beaucoup de francais...je suis tr&egrave;s timide...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 4 ans! Vous parlez bien fran&ccedil;ais alors. Est-ce que vous d&eacute;j&agrave; &eacute;tiez en France? Le monde parle tr&egrave;s diff&eacute;rent que ceux dans la classe <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> je serai en France cet &eacute;t&eacute; pour la vocation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0d31729e3fa2e49018baa583951b792632f4fd","tid":256693,"uid":76926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:45:44.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0418fa05940f623f6915fd4f4d34a2c844e2ee4","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟鐘意學語言但身邊好少人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從上年去完歐遊就鐘意左法國同芬蘭呢兩個國家<br />\n返到香港會日日係屋企聽佢地既歌同上YouTube睇啲片<br />\n之後慢慢開始學佢地既語言同文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nEn fait j'ai appris la langue fran&ccedil;aise il y a plusieurs ans mais cette langue est si dur <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> voulez-vous chatter avec moi en fran&ccedil;ais? <br />\n<br />\nNyt min&auml; opiskelen suomea kotona <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pid&auml;n suomesta kielt&auml; oikein paljon, mutta t&auml;&auml;ll&auml; ei ole ihmisi&auml; kuin min&auml; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMoi. Min&auml; asun Varissuossa</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> jooooo miksi asut varissuossa?? Opiskelet tai olet kotoisin suomalaista? Puhutko puhukielta?"},{"pid":"431b8a90020c226e0e8d3c040f8939d773ac830b","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芬蘭文好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀因爲芬蘭文語法係好唔同<br />\n基本上係世界上無乜共同既語系<br />\n就算鄰近既北歐國家或者俄羅斯都完全同芬蘭文唔同<br />\n只有Estonian 同hungarian 可以算係同芬蘭文相似少少<br />\n而且要學都好難<br />\n我今年1月開始學<br />\n去過誠品同商務都唔見有芬蘭文既書買<br />\n宜家真係靠我芬蘭既朋友寄書比我，上YouTube同埋玩啲學語言既遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有個叫influent 幾好玩，學生字一流<br />\n最近報左aalto university 既online introductory Finnish 6月開始上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但個syllabus 睇過好似太基本，我已經學過晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過免費既都想試下"},{"pid":"2bce3f11716dc0051823d707ae0b86a129eefd9e","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚打老虎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係咪識你"},{"pid":"611d3a3eb7feefc8d25f63fbaa8109b0c214248d","tid":256693,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:56:02.000Z","msg":"其實你地英文好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3be33ad4be57af91c6f6a140073a5fbb1d61ed","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T19:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Salut &agrave; tous, j'ai &eacute;tudie en France pendant plusieurs  ann&eacute;es et donc je peux communiquer en fran&c