r Nazi: <br />\nWie viele Sprachen kennst du? <br />\nUnd es ist sehr sch&ouml;n, dass jemand Finnisch lernen m&ouml;chte"},{"pid":"e8b0af06bb3951574de1c5395017dfa20c8e1dad","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貪心撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且比你更貪<br />\n但實行上黎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598048e39a5793b3b1f87978a162b11af560c456","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"我既短期目標好渺小<br />\n就係用法文聊我以前exchange識過既法國妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5ebc56c303047b5b75fd77b4539e0f17ea4bb2","tid":256693,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"西班牙文+俄文 但2個地方都未去過 想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc40603da36e2b46437bbc65c8f8a78b5ded5b38","tid":256693,"uid":118868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貪心撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且比你更貪<br />\n但實行上黎就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三開我仲頂得順 <br />\n再開多隻文感覺上應該頂唔到<br />\n不過我本身唔係話想學到精<br />\n傾到計我已經夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關好多野就算翻譯左都GET唔到個FEEL"},{"pid":"e8f3b3864f45ae929e8fb4dfb1e35798b8f9e9e5","tid":256693,"uid":102563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上緊法文暑sem<br />\n唉幾時先可以同native溝通到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真係講吳埋 因為佢地講得好快 所以可能writing ok, 但listening oral會係最難"},{"pid":"f00bb3dc86f90abfaed7dd43c8951a28ae2fb9a3","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Salut &agrave; tous, j'ai &eacute;tudie en France pendant plusieurs  ann&eacute;es et donc je peux communiquer en fran&ccedil;ais avec les autres . Maintenant j'enseigne le fran&ccedil;ais &agrave; temps partiel. Moi, j'aime bien la langue et je suis en train d'apprendre l'espagnol<br />\n<br />\nEnchant&eacute;e<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nohhh la la vous &ecirc;tes professeur du fran&ccedil;ais?? Je pr&eacute;f&egrave;re de travailler en France si je pourrais parler bien fran&ccedil;ais comme vous <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> avez-vous pass&eacute; des examens et quel niveau vous &ecirc;tes en ce moment?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNon non  pas vraiment, je ne suis pas prof, mais seulement enseignante priv&eacute;e. Je travaille &agrave; hk pas en France.  En fait tu parles bien fran&ccedil;ais! J'ai pass&eacute; b2 il y a qqls ann&eacute;es et je ne veux pas payer pour c1. Si tu veux travailler en France, peut &ecirc;tre c'est meilleur d'&eacute;tudier l&agrave; pour un an ou qql mois</blockquote><br />\nOuiii j'esp&egrave;re que je pourrais trouver des &eacute;coles en France qui me veulent. Je ne suis que en B1 et c'est pas assez pour &eacute;tudier en Fran&ccedil;ais :( il faut trouver les &eacute;coles en anglais"},{"pid":"ae292b4b7066615da5d56bce42f27416e71bd917","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T07:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Je parle pas fran&ccedil;ais <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSlt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) mais tu parles comme un fran&ccedil;ais"},{"pid":"cbfa7fe734bd5c8f7a93b1c543a3b2a84439caac","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上緊法文暑sem<br />\n唉幾時先可以同native溝通到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩開始學？咁實仲有排先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己學法文真係學得好慢<br />\n唔知係咪因爲個語言本身就好難學<br />\n特別係聽方面要記好多liaison<br />\n好多字都讀音好似，聽完要load好耐先知佢講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如quel, qu'elle, quelle.. ce, se, ceux..."},{"pid":"57cdbd44c09c4b7c577c1929d1e3b5ac18b36a64","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學法文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難唔難？</blockquote><br />\n難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔揾native 練係無可能溝通到<br />\n雖然全部語言一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c400b753f953c8e4774304f8b6249a6e8d8edda","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:12:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁聽都6種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正係日韓既字要學寫都煩<br />\n但始終幾分似中文，應該唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙文同法文都似，如果你本身識其中一種既話應該幾個月就學識第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瑞典文似英文，如果英文好最易學應該呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄文應該係最難！我其實都有學緊，但正係啲s 音都幾十個完全分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400113afc81f2b923de3e86417731a13764764f7","tid":256693,"uid":118127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"英文都未搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06b82e6e46f4c3b4d32212c930cb2e036397449","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Guten Tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGuten tag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ich verstehen ein bisshen Deutsch. Leben Sie in Deutschland?(schei&szlig;e 應該錯晒文法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWie viele Sprachen du kennst <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUnd das ist sehr sch&ouml;n jemand Finnisch m&ouml;chte gelernt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGrammar Nazi: <br />\nWie viele Sprachen kennst du? <br />\nUnd es ist sehr sch&ouml;n, dass jemand Finnisch lernen m&ouml;chte</blockquote><br />\n睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我估你問我識幾多語言？<br />\n暫時有一直keep住學既有英文法文芬蘭文<br />\n以前學過既有日文同俄文<br />\n日文正係識睇同讀啲hiragana katagana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但因為無咩接觸日本文化所以無左個動力<br />\n俄文有上網學，因為報左2018世界杯去俄羅斯做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有個free online course 比d義工學俄文，但之後個網bug 左就無再學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5425dc16543b9648cbb5b4b861eee041d8025100","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:19:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我既短期目標好渺小<br />\n就係用法文聊我以前exchange識過既法國妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncoucou je bande tu veux venir chez moi?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afd4f73c96ec81c0db8a7808713825d24c2f942","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西班牙文+俄文 但2個地方都未去過 想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學語言係一件好漫長既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然最好當然係學左先去果到旅行<br />\n但未去過其實又好難學得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係好矛盾<br />\n我自己覺得去完果個國家之後學果個文既感覺會好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以可以一路學一路去旅行<br />\n有時學果個語言既進度係會慢落黎<br />\n但去完果個國家會有另一番覺悟，無啦啦會突飛猛進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry for 1999 可能學得太多其他文，啲中文差左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79985b39bbed28340b7ccd46a72e30a2c3836434","tid":256693,"uid":118868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:26:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁聽都6種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正係日韓既字要學寫都煩<br />\n但始終幾分似中文，應該唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙文同法文都似，如果你本身識其中一種既話應該幾個月就學識第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瑞典文似英文，如果英文好最易學應該呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄文應該係最難！我其實都有學緊，但正係啲s 音都幾十個完全分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n瑞典文似英文 呢個我都覺<br />\n自從識個人教左我IKEA個瑞典發音 我就好想學"},{"pid":"eb51b31b66948a91e797d076762ad3c85b8af074","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Guten Tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGuten tag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ich verstehen ein bisshen Deutsch. Leben Sie in Deutschland?(schei&szlig;e 應該錯晒文法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWie viele Sprachen du kennst <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUnd das ist sehr sch&ouml;n jemand Finnisch m&ouml;chte gelernt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGrammar Nazi: <br />\nWie viele Sprachen kennst du? <br />\nUnd es ist sehr sch&ouml;n, dass jemand Finnisch lernen m&ouml;chte</blockquote><br />\n睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我估你問我識幾多語言？<br />\n暫時有一直keep住學既有英文法文芬蘭文<br />\n以前學過既有日文同俄文<br />\n日文正係識睇同讀啲hiragana katagana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但因為無咩接觸日本文化所以無左個動力<br />\n俄文有上網學，因為報左2018世界杯去俄羅斯做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有個free online course 比d義工學俄文，但之後個網bug 左就無再學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我學啲文好接近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日文N4都未到，不過N3鳩做MC碌過左<br />\n法文岩學緊第二個course，前路漫漫<br />\n俄文而家我冇上course，上網flirt俄妹進步仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n惟一真係學得似樣少少既只有德文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07f29ee7ff4b6b3216890e8278222bb912f8c38","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我既短期目標好渺小<br />\n就係用法文聊我以前exchange識過既法國妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncoucou je bande tu veux venir chez moi?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌淨係明je, tu, chez moi<br />\n叫佢上我屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc457d63c6be00acd029ee2b4b7f06b7dff5453","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁聽都6種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正係日韓既字要學寫都煩<br />\n但始終幾分似中文，應該唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙文同法文都似，如果你本身識其中一種既話應該幾個月就學識第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瑞典文似英文，如果英文好最易學應該呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas