/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全句 darling I'm hard u wanna come over? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照住講就得啦"},{"pid":"8e93bc7cff6045e342141e8f505621c2015e0529","tid":256693,"uid":58527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Guten Tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGuten tag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ich verstehen ein bisshen Deutsch. Leben Sie in Deutschland?(schei&szlig;e 應該錯晒文法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWie viele Sprachen du kennst <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUnd das ist sehr sch&ouml;n jemand Finnisch m&ouml;chte gelernt <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGrammar Nazi: <br />\nWie viele Sprachen kennst du? <br />\nUnd es ist sehr sch&ouml;n, dass jemand Finnisch lernen m&ouml;chte</blockquote><br />\n睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我估你問我識幾多語言？<br />\n暫時有一直keep住學既有英文法文芬蘭文<br />\n以前學過既有日文同俄文<br />\n日文正係識睇同讀啲hiragana katagana <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但因為無咩接觸日本文化所以無左個動力<br />\n俄文有上網學，因為報左2018世界杯去俄羅斯做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有個free online course 比d義工學俄文，但之後個網bug 左就無再學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我grad左仲想去歐洲讀master，當中就係有呢個任性既原因<br />\n我想去當地浸語言<br />\n而家好想去俄羅斯讀大學俄文foundation<br />\n不過屋企人實唔想我咁做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係想去歐洲讀百展呇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上年grad，本身報左芬蘭大學既master 但前幾日覆我話文件遲到，late application will not be considered <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想死<br />\n好彩仲報多左個但係bachelor黎，我同你一樣好任性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要有機會可以係果邊浸語言讀多個bachelor都無所謂，六月就知佢收唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f707ff17aa496c2ff2beca11e61209768fe7bbb9","tid":256693,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:43:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我既短期目標好渺小<br />\n就係用法文聊我以前exchange識過既法國妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ncoucou je bande tu veux venir chez moi?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌淨係明je, tu, chez moi<br />\n叫佢上我屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係呀 <br />\nCoucou 係懶cute 既hello <br />\nBander 係扯旗既verb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全句 darling I'm hard u wanna come over? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照住講就得啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉屌當年呢個A0法國妹，一個月內就畀個哥倫比亞仔溝左<br />\n果陣我地全部同大家用德文溝通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說我地租約完就黎要搬（佢住我樓上）<br />\n我問佢Wann ziehst du dich aus? <br />\n隔離瑞士妹即刻嚇到指正我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知你地明唔明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b155d58e28d417dea7692f3d43e2cd594a81da2e","tid":256693,"uid":118868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>日 韓用字似中文 而且日同韓文法本身似 所以學緊<br />\n之後想學西班牙文 因為多人用<br />\n仲有法文同俄文 唔知有種莫名其妙地吸引我想學<br />\n仲有瑞典文 因為識人住個邊<br />\n我會唔會貪心左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就咁聽都6種語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正係日韓既字要學寫都煩<br />\n但始終幾分似中文，應該唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n西班牙文同法文都似，如果你本身識其中一種既話應該幾個月就學識第二種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瑞典文似英文，如果英文好最易學應該呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俄文應該係最難！我其實都有學緊，但正係啲s 音都幾十個完全分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n北歐語言我唔知<br />\n但唔計相對小語種，例如匈牙利，烏克蘭呢堆（波蘭，希臘都當埋），俄文難度應該係歐洲大語種之霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只係個有環遊世界夢想嘅小小小男孩<br />\n學語文都係由香港人去得最多嘅日本<br />\n同差唔多最多人用嘅西班牙文 <br />\n慢慢先再推入去<br />\n我都覺俄文應該係我想學嘅之中嘅BOSS<br />\n不過我感覺上最難係阿拉伯語系(只係感覺)"},{"pid":"a342076ab3cb454ba712e7228a753a18c9ef9d37","tid":256693,"uid":118868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Guten Tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGuten tag <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ich verstehen